Description

The BoatCardController class is the controller for the boat card element.

The CardListener interface defines abstract methods to control boat-card, creditCard-card and notification-card elements.
Client
The Client class establishes a connection with the server and manage the communication, sending request and receiving back the responses.
Constants
The Constants class defines constants values used throughout the project.

The Notification class is used to store and manage all the information related to a notification.

Race

Response<T>

Server
Server class manages a concurrent server, which generates a new child process for each incoming client connection.
ServerLoginController
The ServerLoginController class is the controller for the admin login scene.
ServerThread
The ServerThread manages a thread generated by the concurrent server Server to handle an incoming request.
SignFormController
The SignFormController class is the controller for both the SignUp/SignIn scenes.
Staff
The Staff class is used to store and manage all the information related to a staff member of the Yacht Club.

The StaffInterfaceController class is the controller for the Staff Interface.
